# Custom domain for GitHub Pages
# 1. Copy this file to CNAME (remove .example)
# 2. Replace with your domain:
# www.selvendran.dev
# 3. GitHub repo → Settings → Pages → Custom domain → enter same domain
# 4. DNS at your registrar:
#    CNAME  www  →  selvendran254.github.io
#    OR A records for apex (@) → 185.199.108.153 (and .154, .155, .156)
# 5. Enable "Enforce HTTPS" in GitHub Pages settings (SSL auto ~24h)
# 6. Set CUSTOM_DOMAIN in js/config.js to match

www.example.com
